---
title: Glossary of Jamstack Terminology
description: Learn definitions of core terms within the Jamstack ecosystem in this glossary. Check it out!
layout: layouts/base.njk
---


<section class="mt-16">
  <h1>Glossary</h1>
  <p class="w-2/3">A collection of terms often used when talking about Jamstack and associated web technologies.</p>
</section>

<section class="no-underline">
  <ul>
    {% for item in glossary | selectattr("definition") | sortKey("term") %}
    <li class="my-2"><a href="/glossary/{{ item.id }}/">{{ item.term }}</a></li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="border-gray-400 border-b mb-10">
  {{ content | safe }}
  <p class="mt-12 mb-20">You can help us to expand and improve this glossary <a href="{{ pkg.repository.url }}/issues">by creating an issue</a>.</p>
</section>

